Package io.smudgr.extensions.midi.tcp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeviceClient
    The DeviceClient connects to a foreign DeviceServer and notifies a given Device.DeviceObserver of messages broadcasted by the server.
    DeviceMessage
    The DeviceMessage class represents an arbitrary clone-able MidiMessage
    DeviceServer
    The DeviceServer listens to connections and broadcasts MIDI messages to clients.
